OL,3,CFirst Minister responds to Starmer
OL,4,Cresignation
OL,6,FFirst Minister of Wales Rhun ap
OL,7,FIorwerth has called for "a new
OL,8,Frelationship" between Westminster and
OL,9,FWales, following Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,10,Fresignation.
OL,12,FSir Keir set out a timetable for his
OL,13,Fdeparture as potential successor, Andy
OL,14,FBurnham, returns to Westminster
OL,15,Ffollowing his by-election win last
OL,16,FFriday.
OL,18,FOver the past few months, he has faced
OL,19,Fincreasing pressure on his political
OL,20,Ffuture, with more than 100 Labour MPs
OL,21,Fcalling for him to step down.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
